Caleb McLaughlin -LRB- born October 13 , 2001 -RRB- is an American actor .
He began his career on the Broadway stage as Young Simba in the musical The Lion King .
Since 2016 , he has portrayed Lucas Sinclair in the Netflix science fiction drama series Stranger Things .
Industry reports have confirmed that he will return in Season 2 .
In 2017 , McLaughlin appeared in the BET miniseries The New Edition Story as Ricky Bell .